title: Yuezhou Lv Wins The Best Student Paper Award in DISC 2015 (Tsinghua University)
text: ( Source : Tsinghua University ) Yuezhou Lv Wins The Best Student Paper Award in DISC 2015 Yuezhou Lv, a third-year PhD candidate of IIIS , Tsinghua University, won The Best Student Paper Award for his paper Local Information in Influence
